# UI & DaisyUI

- DaisyUI IS installed and actively used — use its classes: `btn`, `card`, `badge`, `modal`, `alert`, `steps`, `countdown`, `drawer`, `dropdown`, `menu`, etc.
- Tailwind v4 via `@import "tailwindcss"` syntax — no `tailwind.config.js`
- Dark mode: `data-theme=dark` / `data-theme=light` (two custom themes defined in app.css)
- Never use `@apply` in raw CSS
- All user-facing text in Spanish
- Use `<.icon name="hero-x-mark">` for icons, never Heroicons module directly
- Use `<.input>` component for all form inputs
- Implement subtle micro-interactions, hover effects, smooth transitions
- Countdown timer for `betting_closes_at` using `Process.send_after/3`
- PubSub topics: `"game_event:{id}"` for race updates, `"user:{id}"` for balance/ticket updates
